    <string name="about_privacy_summary">OpenRec does not use the network, analytics, ads, or cloud storage. Camera and microphone are used only while you record. Videos are stored locally on your device in app-private storage. You can share or delete them at any time.\n\nStealth options (alternate icons, minimal notification) only change how the app appears on your device. They do not transmit data.\n\nYou are responsible for complying with local recording consent laws.</string>
